! $Id: tdiff,v 1.1 2001/12/07 16:54:20 toast Exp $
TDIFF(seconds)
  Returns a string representing the number of seconds passed.

Example:
  tdiff(0)		- Returns "0 seconds"
  tdiff(12345)		- Returns "3 hours 25 minutes 45 seconds"
  tdiff(9825284)	- Returns "113 days 17 hours 14 minutes 44 seconds"

See also:
  FUNCTIONS TDIFF2
